00:09.000 --> 00:16.000
where the flowers blooming and the cherry blossoms in full bloom, and in all the years I've

00:16.000 --> 00:21.000
been here, I don't think the cherry blossoms have ever been more beautiful than they are at the present time.

00:21.000 --> 00:27.000
