00:27.000 --> 00:33.000
of the year is the Cherry Blossom Festival. And the state societies of each of the states

00:33.000 --> 00:41.000
pick a cherry blossom princess. The Tennessee State Society has chosen this year a very lovely,

00:41.000 --> 00:48.000
beautiful girl who hails from Huntsville, Tennessee. And I'm very happy to present and introduce

00:48.000 --> 00:55.000
