19:21.000 --> 19:31.000
The cost during this week we have had quite a number of West Tennessee ins here to testify in connection with the Wolf River Project down in Shelby County.

19:31.000 --> 19:38.000
The Memphis Harbor Project which is also of great importance down there.

19:38.000 --> 19:49.000
